welcome_message_body: Welcome to Oegstgeest, Netherlands! This charming city is known for its beautiful parks, historical sites, and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Oegstgeest has to offer.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Schiphol Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Schiphol Airport, primarily serving low-cost airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: The newest terminal at Schiphol Airport, dedicated to intercontinental flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport. A premium option is also available for faster speeds.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Rotterdam Zestienhoven Airport handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Rotterdam Zestienhoven Airport handles all freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
